tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE anonymized_user_data (
   user_id UUID,
   age INT,
   gender VARCHAR,
   location VARCHAR,
   behavior_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username TEXT,
    first_name TEXT,
    last_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE user_events (
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    event_type TEXT,
    event_date TIMESTAMPTZ,
    event_details JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE purchases (
    purchase_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    product_name VARCHAR(50),
    amount DECIMAL(10,2),
    purchase_date DATE
);
